casebody.data:
WASH FOOTMAN v. STATE OF FLORIDA 23 So. (2nd) 838

June Term, 1945

November 2, 1945 Division A Rehearing denied Dec. 17, 1945 Hendricks & Hendricks, for appellant. J. Tom Watson, Attorney General, and Reeves Bowen, Assistant Attorney General, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

The record and the briefs in this case have been carefully examined and we find no reversible error.

Affirmed.

CHAPMAN, C. J., TERRELL, BUFORD and ADAMS, JJ., concur.
